&lt;BLOCKQUOTE style=&quot;PADDING-LEFT: 5px; MARGIN-LEFT: 5px; BORDER-LEFT: #1010ff 2px solid&quot;&gt;&lt;TT&gt;Nightlight:&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&quot;A clib? is that the bed of babies&quot;asked Nightlight&quot;We can make one, &lt;BR&gt;can&#39;t we? I have some ideas: perhaps if we adapt a pod to her sinze &lt;BR&gt;and programe it that only a maximal could open it, in that way we can &lt;BR&gt;leave to fight camly if predacons attacks... But by now we can leave &lt;BR&gt;her in our bed, we can care her there while we get a crib&quot;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@y...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; : : Rodimus Prime : : &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Rodimus Prime: I think that Elita will sleep now that she is full. &lt;BR&gt;But we really dont have a crib or anything set up for her. &lt;BR&gt;&gt;&nbsp; Airshadow Nightstar &lt;airly2002@h...&gt; wrote: &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Nightlight:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &quot;Just, curiousity&quot;she said while she kissed him and sat down around&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;From: Richard Allen &gt;Reply-To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com &gt;To: &lt;BR&gt;nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com &gt;Subject: Re: Rodimus, Nightlight and &lt;BR&gt;Baby/Flicker and Condor &gt;Date: Tue, 4 Mar 2003 16:23:36 -0800 (PST) &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;: : Rodimus Prime : : &gt;Rodimus took the blanket and covered Elita. &lt;BR&gt;&gt;Rodimus Prime: No, I&#39;m verry happy with our little girl. What made &lt;BR&gt;you ask that? &gt; Airshadow Nightstar wrote: &gt;Nightlight;/Elita: &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt;Nightlight moved quickly and brought a little blanket, she sat down &lt;BR&gt;and give it to Rodimus in order he could cover their baby. She looked &lt;BR&gt;him full of love of them. &gt; &gt;&quot;Would you rather that our baby was a &lt;BR&gt;boy?&quot;said softly &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;From: Richard Allen &gt;Reply-&lt;BR&gt;To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com &gt;To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com &gt;Subject: Re: &lt;BR&gt;Rodimus, Nightlight and Baby/Flicker and Condor &gt;Date: Mon, 3 Mar &lt;BR&gt;2003 21:10:18 -0800 (PST) &gt; &gt; &gt;: : Rodimus Prime : : &gt;Rodimus Prime: &lt;BR&gt;After a infant drinks like she did, you have to burp them. This &lt;BR&gt;prevents any stomcach aches or anything like that. I saw Carly and &lt;BR&gt;Spike, two of the Autobots human allies on Earth, do this to their &lt;BR&gt;son Daniel when he was young. &gt;Rodimus liked the memories that were &lt;BR&gt;coming to him. It was nice when he had been stationed at Autobot City &lt;BR&gt;by Kup, in the mid 1990&#39;s. He, or rather Hot Rod, loved giveing Kup a &lt;BR&gt;hardtime back then. He idolized Optimus. And he found friends in &lt;BR&gt;Spike, Carly, Daniel, Chip and Sparkplug. He had also met Arcee &lt;BR&gt;then... &gt;Rodimus forced himself from any thoughts of Arcee for two &lt;BR&gt;reasons. One: he didn&#39;t want to become angry again thinking of how &lt;BR&gt;she became a Predacon and was killed escaping the very base he was &lt;BR&gt;in. Two: he had a family now. Arcee and anything that was between &lt;BR&gt;them was in the past, the far past. &gt;To reassure himself, Rodimus &lt;BR&gt;gazed at his daughter, then too Nightlight. How lovely she was and &lt;BR&gt;how lucky he was to have met her. How grate it was to, despite being &lt;BR&gt;a millitary commander, finally have a family. &gt; &quot;airly2000 &quot; &lt;BR&gt;wrote:Elita/Nightlight: &gt; &gt;&quot;Why&#39;re you doing that ROdimus?&quot;said &lt;BR&gt;couriously &#39;cause she never &gt;have seen somoeone started to Burp a &lt;BR&gt;baby. &gt; &gt;The baby burped and yawed, she nuzzled against her dad, and &lt;BR&gt;started &gt;to fell sleep. &gt; &gt; &gt;--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard &lt;BR&gt;Allen &gt;wrote: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : : &gt; &gt; Rodimus takes the &lt;BR&gt;bottle away, and starts to &quot;burp&quot; the baby. He &gt;had seen these kind &lt;BR&gt;of actions done by humans when the Autobots were &gt;on Earth. &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;Rodimus Prime: Well thats what it was. She was just hungry. &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &quot;airly2000 &quot; wrote: &gt;Elita/nightlight: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Nightlight moved and &lt;BR&gt;she stayed around Rodimus, Elita was sobbing &gt; &gt; and whinning, she &lt;BR&gt;was hungry. Her sobs lowed when he smelled that &gt; &gt; something was &lt;BR&gt;close... It was food!!. soon she was sucking the &gt; &gt; liquid, with her &lt;BR&gt;little paws she massaged the bottle&#39;s side with &gt;her &gt; &gt; little paws &lt;BR&gt;in a ttempt to get more while a drop of energon &gt;slipped &gt; &gt; and &lt;BR&gt;rolled down her cheek. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Her first sips were quick, but after a &lt;BR&gt;while they were slow and &gt; &gt; stopped to drink. Her eyes looked sleepy &lt;BR&gt;and... started to &gt;hiccup... &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; --- In &lt;BR&gt;nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &gt; &gt; wrote: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; : : &lt;BR&gt;Rodimus Prime : : &gt; &gt; &gt; He smiled and took Elita into his arms. &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;Rodimus Prime: Well she is a Transformer, so I&#39;m going to say &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;Energon. I&#39;ll go feed her. &gt; &gt; &gt; Roddy walked with his daughter too &lt;BR&gt;the kitchen area, and got a &gt; &gt; small bottle of liquid Energon, from &lt;BR&gt;the dispencer. He lets Elita &gt; &gt; drink as she pleased. &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &quot;airly2000 &quot; &gt; &gt; wrote:Nightlight/Elita: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &quot;I think &lt;BR&gt;so...&quot;said Nightlight &quot;Do you know what a baby eats? &gt;I... &gt; &gt; I &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; really don&#39;t know...&quot; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; --- In &lt;BR&gt;nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &gt; &gt; &gt; wrote: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; : : Rodimus Prime : : &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus hea